snippet.title: CellCraft - Learn Cell Biology - GAMES IN EDUCATION (Biology)
snippet.description:
Consider supporting me on Patreon:
https://www.patreon.com/user?u=2318196&ty=h

Hello and welcome to What Da Math. In this video we will discuss a great biology video game that will help you learn about cell biology while still being a fun and challenging strategy game.

Try to finish it and watch the learning process happen by itself!

Learn more by watching the video.

Enjoy and please subscribe.

The game is free here: http://www.biomanbio.com/GamesandLabs/Cellgames/cellcraft.html

Twitter: https://twitter.com/WhatDaMath 
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/whatdamath
Twitch: http://www.twitch.tv/whatdamath

Other videos here: https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PL9hNFus3sjE5uN-jiIk4ZpEbjWVYyaeKb
